The suite we were initially given was on the 6th floor and was very noisy as you could hear the air conditioning from the ground outside.	It would be nice to have a better heater for the room since the fan in the unit is noisy.	Only downside is noise from the extractor fan above the night club next door - just stay on the pool side or high up then there's no problem - staff happy to change rooms.	Also the AC is not very modern and is very noisy.	Only slight downside is some rooms will have noise from the lift shaft as it's a very tall but narrow hotel.